675B1D1F.Line3.121C9F: Today, I leave behind Tomyris. When I don this armor, I continue the name Johanna.

8ED7735D.Line1.121C9F: Yes. My master's armor... here, like common loot. These fools and thieves have no idea what they have.

DF0D9F2A.VoiceDir1.121C9F: Starts joyous. Ends with a bite, disdain
